title: BBQ Lamb Kebabs With Pomegranate Glaze & Tahini Dressing | DJ BBQ
description:
Food Tube's Master of Meat returns with a super-RAD kebab recipe that the gods of heavy metal will be proud of. Tender cuts of lamb marinated in sweet spices with a sticky glaze and gnarly dressing. Guitar solo please! Hello Cleveland!
